summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the City Treasurer to cancel the assessments levied for the improvement of West Frontenac Street and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by watermains and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 3699, and for the improvement of West Frontenac Street and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by grading and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 3767, on certain property which has been deeded for street purposes.
